reviews.reviewText: I love that these are on the bigger side. We did the game where someone can steal your necklace if you say the word baby. It was really easy to string these on to ribbons. You could clearly tell who still had their necklace from across the room, so it was easier to play. The pacis held up well for the duration of the event.These would also make a cute addition to table scatter/confetti or decor for cake or cupcakes. I had never seen it used the bigger ones before this, but this has me converted!
